{"tid":1534760,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"9.7 旅客文宣","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:14:56.000Z","uid":92159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a038a9f1d39a732d04300b6e69c160dbb44a20f1","tid":1534760,"uid":92159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"機場行動會為好多遊客造成不便, <br />\n建議大家係香港<span style=\"color: red;\">各大遊客區做定文宣</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">比遊客</span>有足夠時間<span style=\"color: red;\">準備</span>, 起碼可以book酒店住多晚之類<br />\n<br />\n當然, 一定會有漏網之魚, 但起碼我地做對外文宣可以比外國人睇到香港人係好心嘅, 對比黑警嘅行為, 高下立見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱嘅幫手推推, 講得唔啱嘅就由佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f6a90c96512f21294383a0d9af24bc6a299749","tid":1534760,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7086bf367d68eb880c83e2644c81565e26d8c49a","tid":1534760,"uid":92159,"lik